{"tid":1626758,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［火魔法師留心］唔好再向火堆注入燃料","createTime":"2019-10-05T12:49:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T16:37:01.000Z","uid":80567,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"84c6ce4dbabd9f66915607b0dd2feb1e8c013f04","tid":1626758,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:49:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/102008087858015/posts/132008284857995?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F102008087858015%2Fposts%2F132008284857995%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk3jL6x1fkqqvETpDxuWVMK8%3D&h=ff74867f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/102008087858015/posts/132008284857995?sfns=mo</a><br />\n上片為錯誤示範<br />\n但魔術師好冷靜同專業<br />\n避免咗受傷<br />\n<br />\n正值裝修旺季<br />\n大家應該注意手足安全<br />\n將風險降至最低<br />\n<br />\n原理：<br />\n喺你加油時<br />\n火勢會隨住油柱蔓延至container內<br />\n樽內會因氣壓過大，將一部份燃料推出樽口<br />\n從樽口向前，如影片所見，噴出一波波嘅火舌<br />\n但其實並唔係火舌，而係點著咗嘅燃料<br />\n<br />\n風險1）<br />\n新手魔法師會因受驚<br />\n捉唔實個樽或拋棄個樽<br />\n個樽會四圍噴，波及旁邊嘅人<br />\n<br />\n風險2）<br />\n酒精火係冇咁易撲滅<br />\n一旦沾上皮膚，你就只有等佢燒完<br />\n沾上衣物，唔該馬上除衫<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">守則（TLDR）：<br />\n1. 唔好向火堆加燃料<br />\n不論火堆大小<br />\n不論係小樽火酒定大樽電油<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 任何時候倒燃料<br />\n必須冇人企樽口前面<br />\n以免發生噴射時被波及<br />\n<br />\n3. 施法現場唔好食煙<br />\n有啲燃料係易揮發<br />\n空氣中都可能點燃<br />\n<br />\n4. 避免穿著易燃衣物<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1655000/1659887/clothes_fire_thumb_20170213_J_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1655000%2F1659887%2Fclothes_fire_thumb_20170213_J_600.jpg&h=08aa7560&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n最後大家武運昌隆<br />\n請推比唔止前線小隊<br />\n仲有啱啱轉職嘅火魔法師們<br />\n口頭、文宣，用你嘅方法提醒大家<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n香港人反抗</span>"},{"pid":"d10f4e8abd5efcc2d0c2629ffe8fe0226be4f87f","tid":1626758,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:50:23.000Z","msg":"其實加燃料最佳方法係<br />\n成個樽飛入去"},{"pid":"0e1586be6a21d756bcd899c870b674dd771a1a9a","tid":1626758,"uid":80567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d10f4e8abd5efcc2d0c2629ffe8fe0226be4f87f","tid":1626758,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:50:23.000Z","msg":"其實加燃料最佳方法係<br />\n成個樽飛入去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:55:00.000Z","msg":"細樽可以<br />\n揸一大罐嘅手足真係要倒定<br />\n唔好諗住想補刀"},{"pid":"03c11db6454e6d4a9636e390461d13979e0aa6f2","tid":1626758,"uid":80567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:56:31.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"9a9f9cab62626e5ff608724e5cdfa0e4e9498566","tid":1626758,"uid":325706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:37:01.000Z","msg":"推"}]}